metadata.description:
GM&GN Shanghai New York London
早安,晚安,上海纽约伦敦

[GM&GN Shanghai NewYork London] is a experimental video. We are from different corner of the world and we all deserve to be loved no matter where we are.
Hope u could get the joy and love. Happy Valentine’s Day!

[GM&GN上海纽约伦敦]是一部影像作品。 我们来自世界的不同角落 ，无论我们身在何处，我们都值得被爱。
希望你能获得喜悦与爱意。情人节快乐!GM&GN from Shanghai~


Artist: Cory Lee
Music: Long way to go Miguel Johnson
